!!!
%html
  %head
    %title AwlDev
    %meta{ :name => "viewport", :content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" }
    = csrf_meta_tags
    = stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all"
    = stylesheet_link_tag "home", :media => "all"
    = javascript_include_tag "application"
  %body.preview{"data-offset" => "50", "data-spy" => "scroll", "data-target" => ".subnav"}
    %header#header-wrap.row-fluid.navbar-fixed-top
      #header-top-wrap
        #header-top-inner.row-fluid
          #logo-wrap.span4.offset1
            .span4
              =image_tag("logo.png")
            %h1.span8>
              AWL
          #awl-desc.span7
            %h2.span12>
              クリエイターをもっと自由に。マニアを共犯者に。
            .row-fluid
              %p.span10.offset1
                AWLは、クリエイターとマニアをつなぐ、サブカルチャーに
                %br
                特化したクラウドファウンディングのウェブサイトです。
      .navbar
        .navbar-inner
          .container
            %a.btn.btn-navbar{"data-target" => ".nav-collapse", "data-toggle" => "collapse"}
              %span.icon-bar
              %span.icon-bar
              %span.icon-bar
            = link_to 'AWL', root_path, :class => 'brand'
            %header#main-menu.nav-collapse
              %ul#main-menu-left.nav
                %li= link_to 'projects', projects_path
                %li= link_to 'about us', about_path
                - if user_signed_in?
                  %li= link_to 'Mypage', mypage_index_path(:username => current_user.username)
                  %li= link_to 'Logout', destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete
                  %li
                - else
                  %li= link_to 'Login', new_user_session_path
                  %li= link_to 'sign up', new_user_registration_path
    %div.container
      = yield
